<section class="hero">
  <div class="container hero-grid">
    <div class="hero-copy">
      <p class="eyebrow">Farm-to-market made simple</p>
      <h1>Connect farmers and buyers in one trusted marketplace.</h1>
      <p class="hero-text">
        AgroLink helps farmers showcase fresh produce and helps buyers discover reliable suppliers faster.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/signup/farmer">Join as a farmer</a>
        <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/signup/buyer">Join as a buyer</a>
      </div>
      <div class="trust-row" aria-label="Platform highlights">
        <span>Verified roles</span>
        <span>Direct enquiries</span>
        <span>Local-first sourcing</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-panel" aria-label="Marketplace overview">
      <div class="market-card market-card-main">
        <span class="status-pill">Demo marketplace</span>
        <h2>Fresh supply, clearer demand.</h2>
        <p>Build listings, discover products, and start buyer-farmer conversations.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="floating-card card-farmer">
        <span>Farmer</span>
        <strong>List produce</strong>
      </div>
      <div class="floating-card card-buyer">
        <span>Buyer</span>
        <strong>Find suppliers</strong>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" id="about">
  <div class="container section-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">About us</p>
      <h2>Designed for practical agriculture trade.</h2>
      <p>
		  AgroLink helps verified farmers showcase available produce, manage buyer requests, coordinate delivery or pickup, and maintain trade records. Buyers can search listings, connect with suppliers, request orders, and track activity through a structured digital workflow.
	  </p>
    </div>
	  <div class="feature-grid">
		  <article class="feature-card">
			  <div class="feature-video-row">
				  <span class="feature-video-circle" aria-hidden="true">
					  <video
						class="feature-video"
						autoplay=""
						muted=""
						
						playsinline=""
						preload="metadata"
    >
						  <source src="<%= assetPath('/videos/about_us/for_farmers1.mp4') %>" type="video/mp4" />
					  </video>
				  </span>
			  </div>

			  <h3>For farmers</h3>
			  <p>Create a profile and showcase available products to serious buyers.</p>
		  </article>

		  <article class="feature-card">
			  <div class="feature-video-row">
				  <span class="feature-video-circle" aria-hidden="true">
					  <video
						class="feature-video"
						autoplay=""
						muted=""
						
						playsinline=""
						preload="metadata"
    >
						  <source src="<%= assetPath('/videos/about_us/for_buyers1.mp4') %>" type="video/mp4" />
					  </video>
				  </span>
			  </div>

			  <h3>For buyers</h3>
			  <p>Discover farmers and build a dependable sourcing network for fresh produce.</p>
		  </article>

		  <article class="feature-card">
			  <div class="feature-video-row">
				  <span class="feature-video-circle" aria-hidden="true">
					  <video
						class="feature-video"
						autoplay=""
						muted=""
						
						playsinline=""
						preload="metadata"
    >
						  <source src="<%= assetPath('/videos/about_us/secure_foundation1.mp4') %>" type="video/mp4" />
					  </video>
				  </span>
			  </div>

			  <h3>Secure foundation</h3>
			  <p>Role-based access, secure sessions, CSRF protection, and password hashing are included.</p>
		  </article>

		  <article class="feature-card">
			  <div class="feature-video-row">
				  <span class="feature-video-circle" aria-hidden="true">
					  <video
						class="feature-video"
						autoplay=""
						muted=""
						
						playsinline=""
						preload="metadata"
    >
						  <source src="<%= assetPath('/videos/about_us/ready_to_expand1.mp4') %>" type="video/mp4" />
					  </video>
				  </span>
			  </div>

			  <h3>Ready to expand</h3>
			  <p>The platform is prepared for listings, enquiries, orders, approvals, and future growth.</p>
		  </article>
	  </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section muted-section">
  <div class="container steps">
    <div class="section-heading centered">
      <p class="eyebrow">How it works</p>
      <h2>Start simple. Grow into a full marketplace.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="steps-grid">
      <article class="step-card">
        <span>01</span>
        <h3>Choose your role</h3>
        <p>Sign up as a farmer or buyer so the platform can show the correct dashboard.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="step-card">
        <span>02</span>
        <h3>Build your profile</h3>
        <p>Add farm, organization, location, and product interest information during signup.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="step-card">
        <span>03</span>
        <h3>Connect directly</h3>
        <p>The next build stage can add produce listings, buyer enquiries, and order requests.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-section">
  <div class="container cta-card">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Get started</p>
      <h2>Ready to create your marketplace account?</h2>
    </div>
    <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/signup">Create account</a>
  </div>
</section>
